msgid ""
"In :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration --> Settings --> "
"Digitization`, check the box :guilabel:`Document Digitization` and choose "
"whether :guilabel:`Vendor Bills` and :guilabel:`Customer Invoices` (this "
